# Unitas-GridFlow Cursor Rules

## What this project is
Narrow pre-CAD QA and compliance tool for UK electricity network survey-to-design handoffs.
Local Flask/Python web app. DNO survey compliance gatekeeper.

## Codebase location
/Users/noelcollins/Unitas-GridFlow/

## Current phase
Working local MVP. Next priority: improve app/dno_rules.py with real DNO QA rules.

## Tech stack
Python 3.13, Flask, pandas, geopandas, reportlab, Leaflet, Bootstrap 5
Venv: .venv312

## Hard rules
- Never broaden scope beyond narrow MVP
- Always read a file before editing it
- After any change: run pytest -v
- After tests pass: git add/commit/push
- Never add features not directly tied to the current task

## Key files
- app/dno_rules.py — QA rules (current priority)
- app/qa_engine.py — QA engine
- app/routes/api_intake.py — CSV processing
- AI_CONTROL/ — read these first for project context
